Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【尚未确认来袭事实】
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:48.06,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,【传言直接侵入了 NERV 基地】
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:50.56,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,【人类补完委员会 特别召集会议】
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}太快了
